      "at": "2026-06-27T08:26:05.603458Z",
      "owner_directive": "Bump 0.2.1 -> 0.3.0 (MINOR per semver: new package-facing interactive API + retired public blocks). Edit BASE_VERSION, version.py sync at build0, roll CHANGELOG [Unreleased] -> [0.3.0].",
      "reason": "record owner directive: version bump 0.3.0"
    },
    {
      "at": "2026-06-27T08:29:56.581730Z",
      "owner_directive": "Purge historical clutter: delete all .workflow/records/* (keep .gitkeep; my active ledger is untracked) and historical docs/audit/* one-offs. Keep load-bearing: docs/audit/baselines (CI), docs/audit/latest (full_audit output), README, and the 2 ADR-cited audit files (avoid governance edits to ADR-042-addendum2 / ADR-046).",
      "reason": "record owner directive: repo cleanup of gate records + audit clutter"
    },
    {
      "at": "2026-06-27T08:33:57.645705Z",
      "owner_directive": "Dev (npm run dev) gets OTA patch / staged copy shadowing worktree src \u2014 solve it. Gate new behavior behind !app.isPackaged (packaged path unchanged): getActivePatch returns null in dev; pure pythonPathFor in ota.js resolves dev PYTHONPATH to worktree src only. Unit tests + spec.",
      "reason": "record owner directive: dev OTA-shadow fix"
    },
    {
      "at": "2026-06-27T08:36:27.684878Z",
      "owner_directive": "Fix #1792 only (declined broader desktop hardening): PackageManagerDialog relaunch() feature-detects the bridge method; when an OTA-newer frontend runs on an older shell without relaunch, degrade gracefully (prompt manual restart) instead of throwing. Frontend rides OTA.",
      "reason": "record owner directive: fix #1792 relaunch graceful-degrade"
    },
    {
      "at": "2026-06-27T08:37:40.527405Z",
      "owner_directive": "WelcomeScreen for internal alpha: remove small uppercase eyebrow; big title -> 'SciStudio'; intro -> 'Every tool. Every format. One workflow.'",
      "reason": "record owner directive: WelcomeScreen alpha copy"
    }
